strings: <voice_0x01001CCB><se_high>media princess: He made a decision! I'm a human again! I saw your face<hero>!
<voice_0x01001CCC><se_high>media princess: It was a dream... <hero> Did you hear that?
<voice_0x01001CCD><se_high>media princess: I must admit that I am very disappointed. I believe that after defeating Dumai, the curse should be broken.
<voice_0x01001CCF><se_high>media princess: I don't know where to go.
<voice_0x01001CD0><se_high>media princess: Do you think it has something to do with the curse?
<voice_0x01001CD1><se_high>media princess: I hope that you will return in good health.
